{"tid":1517916,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［重開］要諗長期罷工罷買策略？","createTime":"2019-08-30T05:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T09:43:44.000Z","uid":311907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e3217d790c06b83a1e089e394575962ee299b28f","tid":1517916,"uid":311907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:23:36.000Z","msg":"罷工一日真係無用，要罷一定要長期。罷工人多未但打唔中要害都係無用。政府態越來越強硬，未必咁快跪低。所以要打持久戰（加上等美國通過法案），一定要諗可持續性。<br />\n<br />\n影響比較大: 航空，物流，醫護，公營機構等等<br />\n影響比較小（或未有咁快）：金融後勤？<br />\n<br />\n如果前者作用係後者既好多倍，後者唔罷但捐出部分人工比前者，係咪可持續？<br />\n<br />\n例如做金融無乜負擔搵50K, 捐個20，30K 出黎，起碼支援到兩個罷工手足。<br />\n<br />\n運作方便，有大台易分配但有無可靠人士管理又係一個問題。。無大台，分地區互相幫手但未必統籌到。<br />\n<br />\n對於罷買，係咪應該集中火力，再引發骨牌效應？打中資零售？除左唔買，不合運動令佢地難做生意都係可行。<br />\n<br />\n集思廣益。"},{"pid":"66f923b0dfcc278e9e76b05a079d0e4e8b640db2","tid":1517916,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:23:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mhik2fq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhik2fq.gif&h=7b54c7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8hT9vY2lxR77dvs0GIZdErU%3D&h=5bae6eea\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8hT9vY2lxR77dvs0GIZdErU%3D&h=32ae3b46\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8hT9vY2lxR77dvs0GIZdErU%3D&h=c5aed683\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"5a9a355badf149e65f5da7ec22798c6fd3b7af1a","tid":1517916,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc